类 FakeActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • cn.sharesdk.framework.FakeActivity
  • 直接已知子类:
    EditPage, FollowList, GetInforPage, GetTokenPage, JsonPage, OnekeyShare, PicViewer, Shake2Share

    public class FakeActivity
extends java.lang.Object
    in order to simplify integrating steps, ShareSDK only provides a single Activity (ShareSDKUIShell) for developers to process GUI logic like authorization.
